q: what happens after the white woman looked at the manual
pred: After the white woman looked at the manual, she began to work on the car. She put on a white shirt and a white apron and started to work on the car. She used a wrench to tighten the lug nuts on the car's wheels and then used a tire iron to remove the tire. She then put on a new tire and tightened the lug nuts again. After finishing the task, she took off her apron and put on a red shirt.
